When consuming OZ horse racing market books, what’s the best way to ignore NSW tracks? Hard coded set of venues to check against? If so, does anyone have such a set and wouldn’t mind sharing?

elements.text: When consuming OZ horse racing market books, what’s the best way to ignore NSW tracks? Hard coded set of venues to check against? If so, does anyone have such a set and wouldn’t mind sharing?

text:
Check the Description of the MarketCatalogue object for the following text: “this is a racing nsw turnover charge market”

Their list of tracks has been inconsistent depending on who you ask, so this is the best way.
